[
  {
    "type": "opener",
    "page": "26",
    "id": "linear",
    "secnum": {
      "en": "SECTION 04",
      "zh": "第 04 节"
    },
    "h1": {
      "en": "Linear motion",
      "zh": "直线运动"
    },
    "lede": {
      "en": "MGN9H rails, joints, and idler tabs carry the Y carriage and X beam. These tie the X and Y axes into a CoreXY arrangement.",
      "zh": "MGN9H 导轨、连接件和惰轮支座托起 Y 滑座和 X 横梁，把 X、Y 两轴组成 CoreXY 结构。"
    }
  },
  {
    "type": "wide-top",
    "page": "27",
    "head": {
      "title": {
        "en": "LINEAR MOTION",
        "zh": "直线运动"
      },
      "small": "linear_10"
    },
    "figures": [
      {
        "src": "linear_10_y_exploded_cam0_jwgq.svg"
      },
      {
        "src": "linear_10_y_assembled_cam0.svg"
      }
    ],
    "notes": [
      {
        "h3": {
          "en": "Build two Y rails",
          "zh": "制作两条 Y 导轨"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "The Y axis uses two identical rails. Assemble both the same way.",
          "zh": "Y 轴用两条相同的导轨，做法完全一样。"
        },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:16mm; top:30mm; width:74mm;"
      },
      {
        "h3": {
          "en": "Clean and grease the rails",
          "zh": "清洁并润滑导轨"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "MGN9H rails arrive coated in shipping oil. Wipe it off and pack the carriage with fresh grease before mounting — that's what gives smooth, long-lasting motion. Prep every rail the same way.",
          "zh": "MGN9H 导轨出厂时带有运输防锈油。安装前先擦净，再往滑块里补足新润滑脂——运动才会顺滑耐用。每条导轨都这样处理。"
        },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:120mm; bottom:25mm; width:80mm;"
      },
      {
        "h3": {
          "en": "Let the T-nuts hang",
          "zh": "让 T 型螺母吊着"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Thread an FHCS into every other hole and let its hammer T-nut dangle on the screw tip. Lower the whole rail onto the extrusion slot, then tighten to draw the nuts up snug.",
          "zh": "每隔一个孔拧入一颗 FHCS，让锤头 T 型螺母吊在螺钉尖端。把整条导轨放进型材槽，再拧紧将螺母拉上来夹紧。"
        },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "right:16mm; top:80mm; width:74mm;"
      },
      {
        "h3": {
          "en": "Mind the carriage",
          "zh": "小心滑块"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "The carriage slides off the rail end with little effort, and a dropped one spills its ball bearings — ruining it. Keep it on the rail, and never swap carriages between rails.",
          "zh": "滑块稍一用力就会从导轨端头滑出，一旦掉落，滚珠散落即告报废。务必让它留在导轨上，且不同导轨的滑块切勿互换。"
        },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:16mm; top:90mm; width:60mm; display:flex; gap:4mm; align-items:flex-start;",
        "icon": "info"
      }
    ],
    "bom": {
      "label": {
        "en": "Bill of materials",
        "zh": "物料清单"
      },
      "rows": [
        {
          "component": {
            "en": "Linear rail",
            "zh": "直线导轨"
          },
          "spec": "MGN9H, 240 mm",
          "qty": "2"
        },
        {
          "component": {
            "en": "FHCS",
            "zh": "FHCS（沉头内六角螺钉）"
          },
          "spec": "M3×10",
          "qty": "12"
        },
        {
          "component": {
            "en": "T-nut",
            "zh": "T 型螺母"
          },
          "spec": "M3 Drop-In",
          "qty": "12"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "type": "main-inset-br",
    "page": "28",
    "head": {
      "title": {
        "en": "LINEAR MOTION",
        "zh": "直线运动"
      },
      "small": "linear_11"
    },
    "main": {
      "src": "linear_11_y_exploded_cam1_xjoj.svg"
    },
    "notes": [
      {
        "h3": {
          "en": "Snug the rails between the blocks",
          "zh": "把导轨夹紧在安装块之间"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Adjust the two bottom idlers so each Y rail is held tight between its mount blocks.",
          "zh": "调整底部两个惰轮，让每条 Y 导轨都牢牢夹紧在两侧安装块之间。"
        },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "right:5mm; top:0mm; width:60mm;"
      },
      {
        "h3": {
          "en": "Fix the Y rails, but not tight",
          "zh": "固定 Y 导轨，但不要拧死"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Hold both Y rails in place with the bolts snug, not fully tightened. Only once the X axis is installed and travels smoothly should you torque them down.",
          "zh": "用螺栓把两条 Y 导轨固定到位，拧到贴合即可，先别拧死。等 X 轴装好、移动顺滑后再拧紧到位。"
        },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "right:16mm; top:120mm; width:80mm;"
      },
      {
        "h3": {
          "en": "Tighten from the middle out",
          "zh": "由中间向两端拧紧"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "When you do tighten, start at the center bolt and work outward so the rail beds down flush against the extrusion.",
          "zh": "正式拧紧时从中间那颗螺栓起，依次向两端拧，让导轨平整地贴合在型材上。"
        },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:0mm; top:0mm; width:55mm;"
      }
    ],
    "notesInside": true
  },
  {
