    "notes": [
      {
        "h3": {
          "en": "Straight side toward the motor",
          "zh": "平直面朝向电机"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "The left and right joints are mirrored. Mount each one with its straight side facing the motor.",
          "zh": "左右连接件互为镜像。安装时，各连接件的平直面都要朝向电机。"
        },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:150mm; top:120mm; width:80mm;"
      },
      {
        "h3": {
          "en": "Tighten in a cross pattern",
          "zh": "按对角交叉顺序拧紧"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Run all four screws in finger-tight first, then tighten opposite corners in pairs. This seats the joint flat on the slider instead of tilting it to one side.",
          "zh": "先把四颗螺钉都用手拧到手紧，再成对拧紧对角。这样连接件才能平贴地坐在滑块上，不会偏向一侧。"
        },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:100mm; top:30mm; width:80mm;"
      }
    ],
