          "en": "Check the X beam slides smoothly",
          "zh": "检查 X 横梁滑动是否顺畅"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "The X beam should glide freely along the Y rails. If it binds, realign the Y rails until it runs smoothly, then tighten them from the center bolt outward.",
          "zh": "X 横梁应能沿 Y 导轨自由滑动。若发卡，先校正 Y 导轨直到滑动顺畅，再从中间那颗螺栓向两端拧紧。"
        },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "right:16mm; top:60mm; width:60mm;"
      }
