          "en": "Check both axes move freely",
          "zh": "检查两轴都能自由运动"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "The X rail is now mounted on the X beam. Confirm its carriage slides smoothly along the X rail, and that the whole beam still travels freely along the Y rails. If either binds, realign that rail and retighten from the center out.",
          "zh": "X 导轨现已装到 X 横梁上。确认其滑块能沿 X 导轨顺畅滑动，整根横梁也仍能沿 Y 导轨自由移动。哪一处发卡，就校正那条导轨，再从中间向两端重新拧紧。"
        },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "right:16mm; top:60mm; width:60mm;"
